title: Prophecy News Watch
cleaned_text:
As Democrats Religious Faith Wanes, So Does Support For Israel In the past decade, sympathy for the Palestinians among Democrats has increased from 23% to 49%. Meanwhile, Republican support for Israel has remained consistent at roughly 80%.

Americans Stressed Over Finances - How Will They Handle Coming Recession? Some 70% of Americans admit to being stressed about their personal finances and more than half, or 58%, of all Americans are now living paycheck to paycheck. Over half (53%) of Americans also report not having emergency savings.

Parental Nightmare - State Will Hide Kids From Parents Who Don't Approve Gender Senate Democrats have passed Senate Bill 5599, a breathtaking evisceration of parental rights. The bill would allow the state to legally hide runaway children from their parents if the parents don't consent to their child's "gender transition".

Flower Shop's Refusal To Serve GOP Highlights The Right (Not) To Do Business One florist has decided blood is on the GOP's hands and has vowed to stop accepting jobs from the Republican Party. While liberals applauded the move, some Christians can't help but notice the double standard. How can the Left praise progressives for bringing their views into the workplace, then turn around and sue believers who do the same?

Ezekiel's Bones Live - Nearly Half Of The World's Jews Live In Israel At the start of 2022, there were a total of 15.3 million Jews in the world, 7 million of whom, roughly 46% of all Jews worldwide, resided in Israel, Israel’s Central Bureau of Statistics revealed on Sunday.

President Biden's actions over the past 2 years explain well enough why our emboldened enemies do not fear us, our triangulating allies judge us unreliable, and calculating neutrals assume America is in descent and too dangerous to join.

Global Currency Is Here - IMF Unveils 'Universal Monetary Unit' Or 'Unicoin' A new global currency just launched, but 99 percent of the global population has no idea what just happened. The "Universal Monetary Unit", also known as "Unicoin", is an "international central bank digital currency" that has been designed to work in conjunction with all existing national currencies.

A recent report by Barna Research listed the top reasons people question Christianity. Among those who claim to be Christian, practicing or otherwise, the problem of human suffering (23%) topped the list.
